snippet.title: Pragmatic Entertainment
snippet.description:
Welcome to the channel!

You can expect videos that at least are entertaining, but ideally contain a message that can make life better, truthful and more beautiful. Knowledge with an emphasis on practical application. 

With the right frame of mind almost everything is interesting. Some of my interests include: science, philosophy, psychology, personal growth, literature, and yes... a little politics.

If you like what you see, please subscribe to the channel. This is just the beginning
